title: Felipe Gabuco
text:
Felipe Gabuco (born May 26, 1916, date of death unknown) was a <a href="Philippines">Filipino</a> <a href="Boxing">boxer</a> who competed in the <a href="1936%20Summer%20Olympics">1936 Summer Olympics</a>. In 1936 he was eliminated in the first round of the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201936%20Summer%20Olympics%20-%20Men%27s%20featherweight">featherweight class</a> after losing his fight to <a href="Theodore%20Kara">Theodore Kara</a>.
